text.section:
The Board may issue a limited license to practice hearing aid dispensing only to an individual who:
Except for completing the requirements under § 2-302.1(c) of this subtitle, otherwise qualifies for a license;
Submits to the Board an application on the form that the Board provides;
Satisfies the Board that the individual will practice hearing aid dispensing only within the scope allowed under subsection (c) of this section; and
Pays to the Board the application fee set by the Board.
